        <p>
            Adding the newsrdr button makes it easy for your visitors to subscribe to your Web site or blog,
            resulting in more repeat visitors.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Promote your content</h2>
        <p>
            With newsrdr's excellent sharing features, your subscribers will be able to share your content
            on social media, increasing your brand awareness.
        </p>
      </div>
